
1. ecr creating:
    search ecr --> create --> visibility settings(public) --> Repository name(movies) --> scan on push(enabled) --> create repository.

2. create server & install dcoker:
    * create one server with(t2.medium) 
    * attach IAM role to server.
    * write docker file.
    * install git and docker, clone flipcart repo from github.
    * copy commands form ecr.

3. ecs:(like docker swarm)
    * search ecs --> cluster name(flipcart) --> create cluster.





